# =============================================================================
# TRAILING SLASH NOTE
# =============================================================================
# Trailing slash enforcement is handled by Next.js (trailingSlash: true in next.config.js)
# which generates all static pages as /page/index.html, served with trailing slashes.
# No catch-all redirect needed - Netlify serves the correct files automatically.
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT add "/* /:splat/ 301" - it causes infinite redirect loops
# because :splat captures the trailing slash and then another / is appended.

